# A-E2 inputs are re-fetchable by the sha256 pins in results/summary.json
# (manifest block) — kept out of git to avoid binary bloat. Re-fetch with
# the URLs + revisions recorded in the manifest; fail-closed sha check is in
# run-a-e2.py. wordfreq data files live inside the pip package (pinned by
# version 3.1.1 + data-file sha256).
inputs/tokenizers/*.json

# Large generated intermediates (reproducible from run-a-e2.py).
results/en-surfaces.txt
results/en-mhat.jsonl
results/en-mhat.meta.json
